items.name: IDManager-IDM-2025
items.description: IDM (Internet Download Manager) is a powerful and user-friendly tool designed to accelerate download speeds, manage downloads efficiently, and resume broken downloads. This project is a lightweight and open-source implementation inspired by the functionality of the original Internet Download Manager (IDM) software.
